SQL_STMT_U.val: select v.Variante1,v.Variante2,v.Variante3,v.Variante4,v.Variante5,COUNT(g.idnr) as Bestand from geraete g WITH(NOLOCK) join variante_idnr v WITH(NOLOCK) on (v.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and v.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and v.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and v.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and v.IDNR=g.IDNR) join KUNDEN k WITH(NOLOCK) on (k.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and k.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and k.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and k.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and k.KDNR=g.Betreiber) where g.artikelnummer=':1' and k.Kontoart='W' and g.ModellNummer=:2 and g.Ebene1=:3 and g.Ebene2=:4 and g.Ebene3=:5 and g.Ebene4=:6 group by v.Variante1,v.Variante2,v.Variante3,v.Variante4,v.Variante5
